      .container
        .row
          .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
            h1.brand-heading Helene Lavigne
            p.intro-text
              | Problem finder. Problem solver. 
              br
              //- | Created by Start Bootstrap.
            a.btn.btn-circle.page-scroll(href='#about')
              i.fa.fa-angle-double-down.animated
  // About Section
  section#about.container.content-section.text-center
    .row
      .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
        h2 About Me
        p
          | I like: creating order and efficiency. 
          br 
          |I also like: good coffee, the outdoors and music.    
        p
          | I've spent years in the workplace finding the cracks and making sure that the details that matter don't slip through them. 
        p
          |Stops on the way:  investing 
          i.fa.fa-arrow-right.fa-fw
          span.network-name   marketing 
          i.fa.fa-arrow-right.fa-fw 
          span.network-name   consulting
          i.fa.fa-arrow-right.fa-fw 
          span.network-name   renewable energy
          
