          //- a(href='http://startbootstrap.com/template-overviews/grayscale/') the preview page
          | 
        p
          | The future: coupling the bountiful bundle of I've learned with coding skills. 
          | JavaScript, Node.js, Express.js, HTML, CSS 
          //- a(href='http://gratisography.com/') Gratisography
          //- |  along with a custom Google Maps skin courtesy of 
          //- a(href='http://snazzymaps.com/') Snazzy Maps
          | 
        p
  // Download Section
  section#projects.content-section.text-center
    .download-section
      .container
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
          h2 Projects
          p Check out what I've been working on.
          p Project #1: Starting off on the right foot at 
            a(href='https://g18-lavigne.firebaseapp.com/') My Morning Dashboard
          p Project #2 (as a group): See the gear used by those in the know at  
            a(href='https://noobish.herokuapp.com/') Noobish
          //- a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg(href='http://startbootstrap.com/template-overviews/grayscale/') Visit Download Page
  // Contact Section
  section#contact.container.content-section.text-center
    .row
      .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
        h2 Contact 
        p Want to talk? 
          a(href='mailto:helene@outlook.com') Email me.  
        p
          |           
          //- a(href='www.linkedin.com/in/helenelavigne') Linkedin Profile
        ul.list-inline.banner-social-buttons
          li
            a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg(href='https://linkedin.com/in/helenelavigne')
              i.fa.fa-linkedin-square.fa-fw
              span.network-name Linkedin
          li
            a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg(href='https://github.com/hlav')
